  "_comment_citations": "Citation verification settings. allowed_domains are prioritized, blocked_domains are filtered out.",
  "_comment_content_gap_analysis": "AUTO-FILLED from Step 3 AI term detection! Pipeline saves detected technical_terms here. Leave empty for auto-detection, or manually specify if needed.",
